{"tid":1697596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"James Cameron：「警察」以為其他人比較蠢","createTime":"2019-11-07T03:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T04:13:45.000Z","uid":134071,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"70fb986d11258591743b06b17bd4e0ae1e930222","tid":1697596,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:01:49.000Z","msg":"唔怪得《未來戰士》新一集係美國票房仆到直, 但係香港票房依然勁收.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rrroundmidnight/photos/a.134554167144835/490695998197315/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frrroundmidnight%2Fphotos%2Fa.134554167144835%2F490695998197315%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNfrdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=80bd1231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rrroundmidnight/photos/a.134554167144835/490695998197315/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n午夜翻牆<br />\n昨天 09:55 發佈 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【占士金馬倫：警察以為其他人比較蠢】<br />\n<br />\nDark Fate開畫，票房全面失利，美國的影評也毫不留情，大力批評這是系列的Dark Fate，但占士金馬倫的這段話，倒值得一看，尤其是香港觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n「《未來戰士》系列並不是關於人類被未來來的機器人追殺，它是關於人類每天失去人的觸覺，然後變成了機器，這容許我們殺死及殘暴地對待他人。警察以為警察以外的人都比他愚蠢，比他們弱、比他們邪惡，他們傷害那些他們宣誓過要保護的人民，麻木（desensitize）自己去完成工作。」嘿嘿嘿。<br />\n<br />\n據報，這段話是當年他在DVD Commentary說的。<br />\n<br />\n翻查一下，金馬倫1991年就用Dehumanize等字眼去形容警察，1991年T2上映前，他接受《洛杉磯時報》訪問，說：&ldquo;That, to me, is the most amazing irony considering that the LAPD are strongly represented in &lsquo;Terminator 2' as being a dehumanized force,&rdquo; says Cameron, the film&rsquo;s writer-director. &ldquo;What the film is about, on the symbolic level, is the dehumanization we do on a daily basis.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n1991的洛杉磯發生甚麼事？當時因為種族因素，社會大亂，1991年3月3日發生Rodney King事件：他一個黑人普通市民，駕車被截停，被五個黑警拳打腳踢，被拍攝後在電視播放，但三個月後，五個黑警被判無罪釋放，結果馬上爆發大型暴動。(T2在七月上映)<br />\n<br />\n1994年，美國黑人運動巨星OJ Simpson懷疑殺妻案，被警察在公路追捕，在電視直播，他後來被捕，卻極多證據下被判無罪釋放，就跟前述的種族衝突有關。這是題外話啦，但占士金馬倫原本想找OJ Simpson飾演第一集的T800。<br />\n<br />\n其實，不少電影人很討厭警察，由差利卓別靈開始就這樣。"},{"pid":"12a616abdda0dc52eb1f80c5efcf6a944c5a5504","tid":1697596,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/LdwkBCz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdwkBCz.jpg&h=1d674ac9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"289ed51ec880415e029b86b79302326e5e464868","tid":1697596,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e69eb7417bfd2f09837983e7f4005d0ff1802c4","tid":1697596,"uid":146535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"最後嗰句<br />\n佢地唔記得要保護嘅係咩人"},{"pid":"b3e8821699f7c0fcafb20dc8b07eda5d277e998f","tid":1697596,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579e316803b6dd27df8210fbea492d40b4d88485","tid":1697596,"uid":243380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9e69eb7417bfd2f09837983e7f4005d0ff1802c4","tid":1697596,"uid":146535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"最後嗰句<br />\n佢地唔記得要保護嘅係咩人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"政權囉<br />\n咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e528418aa2760543712d5bd9dd284f5407f70f2d","tid":1697596,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc8ec2785e4c828fd322c20f310d0771d2f51b6","tid":1697596,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:16:16.000Z","msg":"自己比人洗腦話人地無腦"},{"pid":"276705d922fcf9613